nded up <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4713600-downgrading-haverty-furniture-companies-on-accelerating-weakness\">downgrading</a> the company from a \u201cBuy\u201d to a \u201cHold.\u201d This came</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1190446487/image_1190446487.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747523-haverty-furniture-companies-not-cheap-enough-for-an-upgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 22:25:20", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747524", "title": "Rekor Systems: Undeniable Momentum In This Under-Recognized Tech Vendor", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Busy traffic at dusk on the M42 Motorway near Birmingham\" data-id=\"155385262\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1068px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">esp_imaging/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Rekor Systems Overview</h2> <p>The sharp rise in the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SP500</a>) in 2024 was attributed mostly to the \u201cMagnificent 7\u201d stocks, which form a huge chunk of the index. But as 2025 begins and these momentum stocks sell</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155385262/image_155385262.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747524-rekor-systems-undeniable-momentum-in-this-under-recognized-tech-vendor", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 22:20:22", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747506", "title": "Undercovered Dozen: Natera, Lloyds Banking Group, Eaton, Primoris Services +", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Beautiful light for celebration of Festive colorful fireworks display on night sky, isolated on black background\" data-id=\"2184036626\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1239px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2184036626/image_2184036626.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https:/